item.description: Alright it's that time of year again. We are going to meet at the beach again for some great volleyball. We will be putting up the net at 5:00pm and starting soon after setup. Negative behavior is not permitted. We should all help putting up the net if we are available. We should all be having fun! Please everyone that can help putting up the net it would be much appreciated.  It would also be great if a couple people could bring a rake. If you are new to this we would love you to join.  Let's hope the weather is nice and sunny! New people are always welcome and don't hesitate to email me with questions. Please bring a rake if you have one. After we go to Sawyer beach and have a bonfire. If you would like to go to the bonfire and not volleyball meet us at Jenness beach at around 8:30pm. Please post what you will bring. We need food and wood.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be there setting up the volleyball net! Let us know you are there and we will welcome you!
